Products.RichDescription:
Tip Top 9 Grain Original is high in fibre.

Proudly baking since 1958, Tip Top is committed to providing quality bakery products for Aussie families.

Whether it's our soft loaves of bread perfect for making sandwiches, versatile English muffins for breakfast and snacks, or hot dog rolls to feed the masses during footy season, Tip Top has you covered.

It's no wonder the family says…

Good on ya Mum!

Taste the goodness of Tip Top 9 Grain and enjoy the benefits of:

- Low GI for sustained energy.

- High in fibre.

- No artificial colours or flavours.

- 20% of your Daily Target of Whole Grains (Two slices of Tip Top 9 Grain contributes 20% of the 48g Whole Grain Daily Target Intake).

- Source of protein.

Baked fresh.

Products.RichDescription:
What is Natural WonderFibre blend?

Natural WonderFibre blend is the secret behind Wonder Wholemeal's natural high fibre flour as it contains Hi-maize, a natural fibre milled from specially grown corn. This is why Wonder Wholemeal bread is so soft, full of fibre and provides great tasting goodness.

Wonder Smooth Wholemeal + Iron

Deliciously soft wholemeal bread that is packed full of a blend of fibres to help your family get their daily fibre needs.

- High in fibre

- No artificial preservatives

- Very high in whole grains

- Source of protein

- No added sugar

3 Natural Wonder Fibre Blend:

1 Resistant starch

2 Insoluble fibre

3 Soluble fibre
